snippet.title: [Nintendo 64DD] Kyojin no Doshin 1 First Launch
snippet.description: http://64DD.net This is the first launch and introduction of Kyojin no Doshin 1. After the introduction is a short tutorial with Sodoru, the guy at the bottom of the screen who will help you to master the very simple Kyojin no Doshin basis.
